<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:08:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯提议停火135天、以色列从加沙撤军、谈判结束战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/hamas-proposes-135-day-cease-fire-israeli-withdrawal-from-gaza-talks-to-end-war/0000018d-82b3-d6dc-ab9f-cfffb16f0000</link><description>根据哈马斯提出的三阶段停火方案，人质将被换成1500名巴勒斯坦囚犯，被杀人质的遗体将移交给以色列，随着以色列军队的全面撤出，加沙的重建工作将开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 10:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/hamas-proposes-135-day-cease-fire-israeli-withdrawal-from-gaza-talks-to-end-war/0000018d-82b3-d6dc-ab9f-cfffb16f0000</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯驳斥美国的说法，排除以色列在没有巴勒斯坦国的情况下建立联系，结束加沙“侵略”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-rules-out-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-without-independent-palestinian-state/0000018d-829e-d636-adef-cefefe590000</link><description>就在美国国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比表示释放人质和以色列与沙特关系正常化问题是“不同的轨道”的一天后，沙特阿拉伯外交部表示，如果没有巴勒斯坦国，就不会有任何关系</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:37:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/saudi-arabia-rules-out-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-without-independent-palestinian-state/0000018d-829e-d636-adef-cefefe590000</guid></item><item><title>在史前波兰发现的青铜珠宝可能是祭祀品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/bronze-jewels-found-in-prehistoric-poland-may-have-been-ritual-sacrifices/0000018d-7eda-d6dc-ab9f-7fffac880000</link><description>人们认为欧洲青铜时代的海乌姆诺文化不使用金属。但新的研究认为，古代湖床上的青铜首饰可能是代替人类提供的</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-07/ty-article/bronze-jewels-found-in-prehistoric-poland-may-have-been-ritual-sacrifices/0000018d-7eda-d6dc-ab9f-7fffac880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部城市卡夫卡塞姆的一名男子在家中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-his-home-in-central-israeli-city-of-kafr-qasem/0000018d-8230-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de0bc0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯社区凶杀率急剧上升，48 岁男子在家中被谋杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-his-home-in-central-israeli-city-of-kafr-qasem/0000018d-8230-d6dc-ab9f-cf7de0bc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为了空洞的口号和政治利益牺牲了加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</link><description>《纽约时报》有关仍被哈马斯俘虏的以色列人命运的报道对于政界或军事界的任何人来说都不足为奇。家人声称“时间不多了”的说法如今听起来截然不同</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-sacrificed-the-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-for-empty-slogans-and-political-gain/0000018d-8047-d636-adef-ceef8b310000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝调解努力，人质家属加大力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</link><description>哈马斯再次要求结束战争作为达成任何协议的条件，而内塔尼亚胡部分出于政治原因表示反对。即使达成临时协议似乎也还有很长的路要走 ■ 有报道称，在囚禁期间死亡的人质人数比以色列承认的还要多，政府似乎对战争失去了兴趣</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-to-intensify-their-campaign-as-netanyahu-rebuffs-mediation-efforts/0000018d-8003-daa1-a9fd-e20baf6b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提议三阶段停火，首先停止战斗45天以释放平民人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-live/israel-reviewing-hamas-response-to-hostage-proposal-idf-officer-killed-in-gaza/0000018d-8196-d6dc-ab9f-cfff8a840000</link><description>据路透社报道，哈马斯在停火提案中寻求交换囚犯、交换人质以及撤出以色列军队。加沙真菌感染已导致死亡 ■《纽约时报》报道：以色列正在评估加沙是否有至少 20 名人质被杀，以及 32 人确诊死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 03:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-live/israel-reviewing-hamas-response-to-hostage-proposal-idf-officer-killed-in-gaza/0000018d-8196-d6dc-ab9f-cfff8a840000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院未能通过共和党向以色列提供 170 亿美元独立援助的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-fails-to-pass-gop-effort-to-provide-israel-with-17b-in-standalone-aid/0000018d-80c6-d6dc-ab9f-cfffec3b0000</link><description>鉴于参议院民主党人坚持将以色列援助纳入拜登总统的国家安全补充援助计划（其中包括超过 140 亿美元的以色列援助），该法案获得推进的机会为零</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:58:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-fails-to-pass-gop-effort-to-provide-israel-with-17b-in-standalone-aid/0000018d-80c6-d6dc-ab9f-cfffec3b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心冒犯宗教预备役军人，以色列国防军取消了女性表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-cancels-womens-performance-for-fear-of-offending-religious-reservists/0000018d-8059-daa1-a9fd-e25b6ce40000</link><description>驻扎在北部的该营的士兵们请求举办一场退役派对，其中包括爱情旅的表演，但最终却得到了右翼演讲者和一名恐同拉比的一系列讲座。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-cancels-womens-performance-for-fear-of-offending-religious-reservists/0000018d-8059-daa1-a9fd-e25b6ce40000</guid></item><item><title>美国对极端主义定居者的制裁使以色列极右翼财政部长陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-on-extremist-settlers-put-israels-far-right-finance-minister-in-a-bind/0000018d-801b-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f01d60000</link><description>以色列国民银行冻结了四名涉嫌暴力定居者之一的账户后，财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇誓言要采取行动，但他所能做的就是试图说服美国当局，因为他在美国不受欢迎</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sanctions-on-extremist-settlers-put-israels-far-right-finance-minister-in-a-bind/0000018d-801b-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f01d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列寻求切断加沙对近东救济工程处的依赖，但尚不清楚谁可以取代它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-to-sever-gazas-dependency-on-unrwa-but-its-unclear-who-could-replace-it/0000018d-8059-d636-adef-ceff82270000</link><description>这一想法是试图切断哈马斯与进入加沙地带的人道主义援助的联系的一部分。但消息人士称，潜在的替代者世界粮食计划署在加沙缺乏必要的基础设施来代替该机构的活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-to-sever-gazas-dependency-on-unrwa-but-its-unclear-who-could-replace-it/0000018d-8059-d636-adef-ceff82270000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列问题上，拜登继续选择胡萝卜而不是大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/biden-keeps-on-choosing-the-carrot-over-stick-when-it-comes-to-israel/0000018d-7f91-d636-adef-7fffb8290000</link><description>对于那些希望拜登最终利用军事援助作为筹码的人来说，参议院的一揽子计划还有很多不足之处</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 21:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/biden-keeps-on-choosing-the-carrot-over-stick-when-it-comes-to-israel/0000018d-7f91-d636-adef-7fffb8290000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生的以色列军官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-officer-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-8016-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f95a20000</link><description>大卫·沙库里少校是陆军第401装甲旅作战工程兵第601营副营长。他的朋友这样评价他：“一位举止冷静的指挥官，树立了榜样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 21:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-officer-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting/0000018d-8016-d6dc-ab9f-cf7f95a20000</guid></item><item><title>海法市迫于压力阻止有关以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的新书发行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-thwarts-book-launch-on-israeli-palestinian-conflict-amid-pressure/0000018d-7fa2-daa1-a9fd-7faa3d1c0000</link><description>在市内政党的压力下，市政府宣布“推迟活动”，但没有确定新的日期。民权协会猛烈抨击此举，而右翼分子则赞扬此举</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 20:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-thwarts-book-launch-on-israeli-palestinian-conflict-amid-pressure/0000018d-7fa2-daa1-a9fd-7faa3d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>在人质交易方面，保持权力始终是内塔尼亚胡最关心的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/when-it-comes-to-hostage-deals-staying-in-power-is-always-netanyahus-paramount-concern/0000018d-7fbe-d636-adef-7ffeaf910000</link><description>从 1985 年开始，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在其政治生涯中参与了三起人质交易。他对与哈马斯潜在的新人质交易的立场仍然是个谜，但他肯定会研究民意调查，为自己找出最佳选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:50:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/when-it-comes-to-hostage-deals-staying-in-power-is-always-netanyahus-paramount-concern/0000018d-7fbe-d636-adef-7ffeaf910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列审查哈马斯对加沙停火、人质协议的反应；拜登：“似乎有点过头了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/israel-reviews-hamas-response-to-hostage-deal-biden-seems-a-little-over-the-top/0000018d-7f91-d6dc-ab9f-7ffd246e0000</link><description>在与最近一次访问中东的美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯会面后，卡塔尔总理补充说，哈马斯的反应“总体上是积极的”。他没有提供更多细节，但指出哈马斯对拟议交易有“评论”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/israel-reviews-hamas-response-to-hostage-deal-biden-seems-a-little-over-the-top/0000018d-7f91-d6dc-ab9f-7ffd246e0000</guid></item><item><title>第一批定居者，现在是网络：美国威胁取消间谍软件制造商的入境签证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/first-settlers-now-cyber-u-s-threatens-to-cancel-entry-visas-for-spyware-makers/0000018d-7f25-daa1-a9fd-7f2fd9640000</link><description>尽管美国长期以来一直寻求遏制间谍软件公司，并将 NSO 和 Intellexa 等公司列入黑名单，但以色列进攻性网络行业的消息人士表示，新政策是拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间紧张关系的一部分</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 19:30:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/first-settlers-now-cyber-u-s-threatens-to-cancel-entry-visas-for-spyware-makers/0000018d-7f25-daa1-a9fd-7f2fd9640000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯访问以色列：预计将讨论人质谈判、加沙计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-visits-israel-expected-to-discuss-hostages-gaza-war-and-day-after-plans/0000018d-7ee0-d636-adef-7eeecd300000</link><description>这是美国国务卿自10月7日以来第五次访问中东，美国和以色列正在考虑哈马斯对人质和停火协议的反应</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 18:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-visits-israel-expected-to-discuss-hostages-gaza-war-and-day-after-plans/0000018d-7ee0-d636-adef-7eeecd300000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 123 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f91-daa1-a9fd-7f9b7eba0000</link><description>据以色列国防军、《纽约时报》报道，加沙剩余人质中至少有 32 名人质死亡 ■ 哈马斯对人质释放/停火协议作出“积极”回应 ■ 据报道，以色列向美国和联合国施压，要求允许近东救济工程处继续向加沙提供援助 ■ 绝大多数的以色列人认为下一次选举应该更早举行 ■ 战争结束 123 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f91-daa1-a9fd-7f9b7eba0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 123 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f86-d636-adef-7fee8ff00000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，根据以色列国防军的评估，加沙剩余人质中至少有 32 名人质死亡 ■ 哈马斯表示，它对拟议的人质释放/停火协议做出了“积极”回应 ■ 据报道，以色列正在向以色列施压美国和联合国允许近东救济工程处继续向加沙提供人道主义援助 ■ 绝大多数以色列人认为下一次选举应该比指定日期 2026 年 11 月早得多举行 ■ 这是战争结束 123 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 17:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-06/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-123/0000018d-7f86-d636-adef-7fee8ff00000</guid></item></channel></rss>